2026-06-16  Arc 5 O&C 12.9-12.11 implemented: new `collaborators` table (+ recording on co-membership, both directions, and a backfill); list_collaborators reads it so past collaborators persist — shown muted/no-count and sorted last; past-only "Remove from My Collaborators" with inline confirm; the pane menu is now a native top-layer popover (no more rail-scroll clip). Unit tests green; in-browser check 13.7 pending.
2026-06-16  Tweak (item 12.6/12.8): drag-to-assign rejection toast now names the real reason — "you can only assign the people handed to you here" when a viewer+ picks someone outside their pool, vs. "can't assign people to that task" when the task isn't theirs to staff — replacing the misleading "You can't assign someone there."
